## Usage Instructions

1. Replace `[EntityName]` with the actual entity name
2. Replace `[TableName]` with the database table name
3. Replace `[EntityDescription]` with a description of what the entity represents
4. Replace `[PropertyName]` with the actual property name
5. Replace `[PropertyDescription]` with a description of the property
6. Replace `[MaxLength]` with the appropriate maximum length
7. Add additional properties as needed
8. Add navigation properties for related entities
9. Consider adding validation attributes as appropriate
10. Always default to Postgres standards

## Common Validation Attributes

- `[Required]` - Field is required
- `[StringLength(max)]` - Maximum string length
- `[Range(min, max)]` - Numeric range validation
- `[EmailAddress]` - Email format validation
- `[Phone]` - Phone number format validation
- `[RegularExpression(pattern)]` - Custom regex validation
